quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  26,176,The thicket`s/dense tangled trees` owners/friends/company denied the messengers
  26,177,"When/if Shu`aib said to them: \"Do you not fear and obey"
  26,178,That I am for you a faithful messenger
  26,179,So fear and obey God and obey me
  26,180,"And I do not ask/beg you on it from a wage/fee/reward, that truly my wage/reward (is) except on the creations all together`s/(universes`) Lord"
  26,181,"Fulfill/complete the measurement/weight, and do not be from the reducers/decreasers (cheaters)"
  26,182,And weigh/measure with the scale/measure the balanced
  26,183,"And do not reduce/cheat the people (of) their things, and do not corrupt in the earth/Planet Earth corrupting/disordering"
  26,184,"And fear and obey who created you, and the nation/creation, the first/beginners"
  26,185,"They said: \"Truly/indeed you are from the bewitched/enchanted"
  26,186,"And you are not except (a) human similar/equal to us , and that truly we suspect you (are) from (E) the liars/falsifiers"
  26,187,So drop on us pieces from the sky/space if you were from the truthful
  26,188,"He said: \"My Lord (is) more knowledgeable with (about) what you make/do"
  26,189,"So they denied him , so torture (of) the shade`s day/time punished/took them, that it truly was a great day`s/time`s torture"
  26,190,That in that (is) an evidence/sign/verse (E) and most of them were not believing
  26,191,"And that your Lord He is (E) the glorious/mighty , the merciful"